'''夏尔·佩罗'''（Charles Perrault，{{bd|1628年|1月12日|1703年|5月16日|catIdx=G}}）是十七世纪[[法国|法国]]诗人、作家，以其作品《[[鵝媽媽的故事|鵝媽媽的故事]]》而闻名。他出生于一个富裕家庭，是家中七个孩子中最小的。1695年，67歲的夏尔·佩罗因失業而投身寫作，兩年後出版了《鵝媽媽的故事》。這本書使得他迅速成名，並在後世被視為現代童話故事的奠基人。<ref>{{cite book|last=Neil|first=Philip|author2=Nicoletta Simborowski|title=The Complete Fairy Tales of Charles Perrault|url=https://archive.org/details/completefairytal0000perr|publisher=Houghton Mifflin Harcourt|year=1993 |page=[https://archive.org/details/completefairytal0000perr/page/126 126] |isbn=0-395-57002-6}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2016/jan/12/who-charles-perrault-google-doodle |title=Charles Perrault: the modern fairytale's fairy godfather |last=Flood |first=Alison |date=2016-01-12 |website=The Guardian- Books |publisher=The Guardian |access-date=2016-01-12 |quote=The stories...might have been old, but what he did with them was new. |archive-date=2020-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326054032/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2016/jan/12/who-charles-perrault-google-doodle |dead-url=no }}</ref>

